Manga List

https://www.mangaeden.com/api/list/[language]/
https://www.mangaeden.com/api/list/0/


[language] 	0 : english
			1: italian

The full json result is 6.4 mb

ex:
{
      "a": "flower-dream", 														// alias
      "c": [																	// category
        "Action",
        "Adventure",
        "Drama",
        "Sci-fi",
        "Supernatural"
      ],
      "h": 1196, 																// hits
      "i": "5372389645b9ef5a0b1d20d8", 										    // ID
      "im": "ad/ad8dbe2c909de99899f1015a360f75e3ced31023672d6ff0d2b7547c.jpg",  // image
      "ld": 1416420134.0, 														// last chapter date
      "s": 2, 																    // status
      "t": "Flower Dream"														// title
    },

