Manga info and chapters list

https://www.mangaeden.com/api/manga/[manga.id]/

Note: boku no hero’s id = 541aabc045b9ef49009d69b6
https://www.mangaeden.com/api/manga/541aabc045b9ef49009d69b6/

	Chapter array element explained
[
143,											                                // Chapter number
1498736263,									                                    // chapter’s date (epoch)
"C’mon, Rappa, Let’s Have Ourselves a Match!!",		                            // chapter’s title
"5954e687719a1640af7fe232"					                                    // chapter’s id
],

